ria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarterfinals\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a chance to make history, the Nigerian team took the court against the gold standard of women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hoops.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5940977561132319, \"rank\": 0.6823883510136293, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold standard\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"hoops\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they did not prevail, they put up a fight, and their run was both inspirational and a disclaimer \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 African women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s basketball has arrived.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fight\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"their run\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"a disclaimer \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 African women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s basketball\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s no secret that the American team has come out sluggishly in each of its three group phase games.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_L