resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three Aces players\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the starting lineup\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"a bucket\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening possession\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"a standstill\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chelsea Gray missed yet another open jump shot, as she is yet to make a basket outside of the paint in this Olympics.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chelsea Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Gray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another open jump\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"a basket\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the paint\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympics\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kalu had trouble getting going as well, in large part due to Young\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s stifling defense.\\u00c2 After three minutes, the score was knotted up at 2-2 until Gray found Breanna Stewart for a basket to break the dry spell.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Breanna Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re